      "id": "PopularPost364388",
      "post_content": "You know, it's kind of interesting, and confusing, that you can have this card, [Karn, Silver Golem](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Karn, Silver Golem) and [Legacy Weapon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Legacy Weapon) on the battlefield at the *same time*.  \n  \nMy head-canon for that? Karn is using some very advanced and confusing [temporal](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=240133) [manipulation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=6548).",
      "posted_by": "Tiggurix",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost364388\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">You know, it's kind of interesting, and confusing, that you can have this card, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Karn, Silver Golem\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Karn, Silver Golem\">Karn, Silver Golem</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Legacy Weapon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Legacy Weapon\">Legacy Weapon</a> on the battlefield at the <i>same time</i>.<br/><br/>My head-canon for that? Karn is using some very advanced and confusing <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"240133\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=240133\">temporal</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"6548\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=6548\">manipulation</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '364388'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy36920\">Tiggurix</span>\r\n                                (2/19/2014 10:18:01 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubConte