    {
      "id": "PopularPost160455",
      "post_content": "Worst case, he's an over priced yet non color restricted [Vindicate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vindicate)ish with an added bonus and still FAR better than [Spine of Ish Sah](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spine of Ish Sah) in almost any scenario! But at best, well.. at best he's [Karn](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Karn), and IF you're Karn, that makes you, straight. F'in. BRUTAL! O\\_O But you're not Karn. You're not even a Silver Golem.. In fact, you're not EVEN Silver OR Golem.. You're just liberated. But you shouldn't be. Cause you don't appreciate it. No, no you dont.. Not REALLY.. It was WASTED on you.. you ungrateful little.. Just kidding, I love you! :D",
      "posted_by": "Mike-C",
